column2: select p.objid as name, p.ra, p.dec                from photoObj p                join dbo.fgetnearbyobjeq(#,#,#) n on p.objid=n.objid                join specObj s on p.objid=s.bestobjid                where p.petrorad_r > # and p.r < #                and s.sClass=&&&                and s.z >= #
